videos.description: South Carolina Brandon Edwards returns a punt to Texas A&M territory, but is hit by the Aggies, Braden Mann and fumbles; the Aggies recover.
videos.headline: Texas A&M Punter Mann forces fumble

videos.description: On 3rd-and-goal, South Carolina QB Jake Bentley tries to throw an over-the-shoulder pass that is short and intercepted by the Aggies Charles Oliver.
videos.headline: Bentley's end zone interception stalls drive

videos.description: Texas A&M QB Kellen Mond fakes the handoff and rips a pass to Jace Sternberger for a 4-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Aggies' Mond to Sternberger for a 4-yard TD

videos.description: Ty'Son Williams follows his blockers and bursts for a 27-yard run to put South Carolina in the red zone.
videos.headline: Williams 27-yard run puts Gamecocks in the red zone

videos.description: The Aggies Jace Sternberger grabs and goes for 57 yards to give the Aggies a 1st-and-goal.
videos.headline: Sternberger puts Aggies in red zone with 57-yard catch

videos.description: Jake Bentley fakes the run and finds Shi Smith for a 22-yard touchdown and later finds Bryan Edwards to convert a 2-pt conversion to cut the score to 16-8.
videos.headline: Gamecocks' Bentley connects with Smith for a 22-yard TD

videos.description: On a flee-flicker, Gamecocks' QB Jake Bentley finds Chavis Dawkins for a 33-yard TD and later finds Bryan Edwards again to tie the game at 16.
videos.headline: Bentley launches 33-yard TD to Dawkins

videos.description: Aggies' Kellen Mond rips a pass to Camron Buckley, which is broken up by the Gamecocks' Rashad Fenton to keep the game tied.
videos.headline: Gamecocks'  Fenton breaks up potential touchdown pass

videos.description: Aggies' Trayveon Williams punches in a 3-yard touchdown to seal a 26-23 win for Texas A&M.
videos.headline: Williams' TD secures win for Texas A&M

videos.description: With a minute left in the game, ,QB Jake  Bentley connects with Deebo Samuel for a 6-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Bentley finds Samuel for a 6-yard TD late in 4th
